(26,	1420,	'J. O.',	'randomemail@email.com',	'',	'180.190.115.236',	'2017-09-12 21:56:01',	'2017-09-12 21:56:01',	'I know that I was not one of your best student Sir, failing my OPESYS back in 2014, but I wish you could have stayed, I have wasted so much time prioritizing unimportant things in my life. Now that the time has come that I want to take the COMSEC track under your tutelage, you are now gone, thank you for being my Professor in two of subjects. I hope life fairs well for you Sir. the last time I spoke to you was in a symposium speaker about social jackers - J. O. / J. C.',	0,	'1',	'',	'',	0,	0),
