strong>\n\nI always consider December as a thanksgiving month. It\'s not the food and the prizes in Christmas parties that I enjoy. What I enjoy in Christmas parties is that I am able to see and chat with friends and relatives that I haven\'t seen for some time. Also, it\'s gift giving too! I\'m glad that I have a little extra money to buy gifts for everybody in my list. :)\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_330\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"225\"]<a href=\"https://justinpineda.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10390494_900327666652729_6411674974913808440_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-330\" src=\"https://justinspeaks.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/10390494_900327666652729_6411674974913808440_n.jpg?w=225\" alt=\"Consolation prize from the Parol Making Contest\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a> Consolation prize from the Parol Making Contest[/caption]\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_331\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://justinpineda.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10846372_10152417861385951_3340181129200935836_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-331\" src=\"https://justinspeaks.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/10846372_10152417861385951_3340181129200935836_n.jpg?w=300\" alt=\"Coca-Cola Christmas Party (Photo by Sheryll)\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a> Coca-Cola Christmas Party (Photo by Sheryll)[/caption]\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_332\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://justinpineda.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10846495_10152417864335951_7685654961106850244_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-332\" src=\"https://justinspeaks.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/10846495_10152417864335951_7685654961106850244_n.jpg?w=300\" alt=\"Coca-Cola Christmas Party (Photo by Sheryll)\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a> Coca-Cola Christmas Party (Photo by Sheryll)[/caption]\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_333\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://justinpineda.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/10858003_10152411978610951_7